        <li>
          <strong>ABA Consulting (Project Manager):</strong> managed strategy
          engagements for Fortune 500, foundation, and nonprofit clients,
          leading analyst teams of 5 to 8 from scoping through executive
          delivery.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>IKEA (Market Strategy Consultant, contract):</strong>
          assessed financial-services market-entry feasibility, building
          customer segmentation models and competitive dashboards from a
          1,500+ respondent survey.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>The Assistance Fund (Project Manager, contract):</strong>
          led a team of 5 through a 20-week growth engagement with 100%
          on-time delivery, validated by 15+ expert interviews and a 3,000+
          respondent survey.
        </li>
      </ul>

